729
00:46:02,402 --> 00:46:03,431
<font color="yellow">It's just strange.</font>

730
00:46:04,011 --> 00:46:05,794
<font color="yellow">My dad liked you a lot.</font>

731
00:46:05,794 --> 00:46:09,326
