762
00:48:14,629 --> 00:48:16,120
<font color="yellow">That's going to be six years.</font>

763
00:48:18,547 --> 00:48:20,098
<font color="yellow">What are you going to do, Hye Jung?</font>

764
00:48:20,518 --> 00:48:23,908
